transcription.text:
Speaker 1: Hi, this is Viagra.

Speaker 2: Yes, hello. Yes, I'd like to cancel my prescription please.

Speaker 1: Okay, let me pull the prescription here. Mr. Robert Linat?

Speaker 2: Yeah.

Speaker 1: Okay. Alright, so I see that you have a prescription—I mean your account, you don't have any refill at the moment, but you've been receiving Viagra under milligram 25 tablets and you just—

Speaker 2: Don't need it. You just want to order as needed?

Speaker 1: No, I don't want to order no more. I want you guys to cancel my account.

Speaker 2: Okay, let me cancel that for you.

Speaker 1: Alright, so I'll cancel the prescription. Be advised, you know, if you try to reorder in the future, price will be different, but you all set?

Speaker 2: Okay, everything's canceled.

Speaker 1: Okay, okay, because I was set up to deliver again on March, I believe, you know.

Speaker 2: Yeah, yeah, but all of that is canceled now.

Speaker 1: It's all canceled.

Speaker 2: Okay, thank you, I appreciate it.

Speaker 1: Okay, bye bye.
